snippet.title: Beloved Rapture Trailer 2 - Teaser
snippet.description:
This is it!! Our final day on #Kickstarter!

Well, it's been quite the wild ride! I started off skeptical we'd even be funded, and now we've just surpassed our second stretch goal with the third in sight! 

Campaign: http://kck.st/302mtjT 

#IndieGame #16Bit #RPG #PixelArt #SNES
